caller_intent: Heather Johnson from Alliance Insurance is reaching out to Vivian to check if she needs assistance after a previous upset call and to inform her about the closure of the Walnut Cove office due to an emergency.
resolution_steps: Heather explains that Walnut Cove has been closed due to an emergency and is out of their control.
She informs Vivian the office will reopen next Monday and offers to assist if she needs to visit.
Provides her direct phone number for follow-up.
knowledge_required: Awareness of office closure due to emergency
Ability to provide alternative assistance options
summary: Heather Johnson from Alliance Insurance contacted Vivian to check on her well-being after a previous upset call and to inform her about the temporary closure of the Walnut Cove office. She offered assistance and provided her contact number for further communication.
